expression: "get_subcommand_help(\"debug\")"
---
Debug policy enforcement: view logs, replay commands, inspect sandbox

Usage: debug <COMMAND>

Commands:
  log      View audit log entries
  replay   Re-evaluate a command against the current policy
  sandbox  Show sandbox enforcement details for a command
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
